trans-unit.source: BGE Balkan is a regional StarCraft II circuit that takes place every week. Players from the Balkan region compete in a series of matches to earn points and prizes.

The circuit is open to all players from the Balkan region, and it's free to participate. The top players from each week will earn points that will count towards guaranteed €150 prize pool at the end of the month.
50% of all donations during game days are added on top of the guaranteed prize pool for the month. You can donate through:
Matches are played on the EU server, and players are required to join the BGE Balkan Discord to communicate with the admins and other players. See the full Rulebook for more information.

Bellum Gens Elite is a premier esports LAN event organized in Bulgaria. Ancient history and traditions, and beautiful scenery combine with high-level action-packed esports competition to bring you an unforgettable experience.
Join us live on for Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora 2025!
Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora returns in 2025 for another epic showdown!
€10000 prize pool and 1 slot at the EWC 2025 StarCraft II finals
The top placing player at BGE Stara Zagora 2025, who has not already qualified for EWC from a previous qualification event, earns a spot at the EWC 2025 StarCraft II.
Yoon "trigger" Hong qualified with a top seed spot.
Joseph "Future" Stanish qualified with a bottom seed spot.
Cho "Maru" Seong-ju and Park "Zoun" Han-sol qualified with top seed spots.
Kim "Ryung" Dong-won and Lei "Rex" Hao-chen qualified with bottom seed spots.
UPDATE: Cho "Maru" Seong-ju and Lei "Rex" Hao-chen forfeited their spots.
Kevin "Harstem" Koning qualified with a top seed spot.
Nikita "SKillous" Gurevich, Yakov "YoungYakov" Moiseenko, Piotr "Spirit" Walukiewicz, Julian "Lambo" Brosig qualified with bottom seed spots.
Peycho "Nitix" Ivanov qualified with a bottom seed spot.
22:30: LIVE DJ Afterparty at Palikari Bar

The Summer Theater in Stara Zagora is located at the foot of largest city park in Bulgaria. This open-air masterpiece combines nature and ancient traditions with modern architecture into a unique experience for the audience.

This is the perfect place for you to experience StarCraft 2 duels of the highest level. Players clash like gladiators on the open-air stage of this gorgeous theater and you are presented with the opportunity to meet your favorite pros face-to-face along the alleys of the beautiful park the venue is located at.

The city hosting this event has more than 8000 years of history! Ancient forums, Roman murals and mosaics, 2000-year-old theaters, bath houses, and aqueducts, it's all beneath your feet and everywhere around you. Traditions and modern esports come together at this unique place!

Bellum Gens Elite Balkan weekly online circuit launches in November 2024 and presents every player in the Balkan region with the opportunity to participate in weekly online matches to earn points towards cash prizes.
Open to everyone in the Balkan region
Compete weekly to earn points towards monthly cash prizes
Bellum Gens joined forces with the Bulgarian StarCraft League and Stara Zagora Municipality to deliver an epic esports experience!
Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora 2020 brought the top Counter-Strike talent in the region to compete under one roof for a prize pool of $10,000!
Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora was one of the few LAN events held in 2020 and due to Covid-19 lockdowns and travel restrictions, only 10 teams were able to participate in the LAN finals.
Bellum Gens offers wide exposure to sponsors and partners via its digital channels and on-side during offline events.
Contact us if you wish to sponsor this or any of the other event organized by Bellum Gens. Our social media contacts can be found at the footer of the page.

Bulgarian StarCraft League a one of a kind StarCraft II league in Bulgaria and are contributing to the development of Bulgarian talent in this esport! All StarCraft 2 games in the Esports Business League are casted by the them!
Stara Zagora is a 6000+ year-old city in the center of Bulgaria. We partner with Stara Zagora Municipality for the Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora premier esports event!

Registrations are restricted to participants from the countries in the selected region. Registrations have no age restrictions. Registrations for this event are not in any way binding and participation can be halted by the registrant at any point of time. Registrations can also be deleted by the user through the user profile settings menu.

Registrations show intent for participation, but participation would require timely check-ins and being on-time for the matches. All applicants must reside in one of the listed countries. If an applicant is discovered to permanently reside outside of the listed countries for the region, that would lead to permanent disqualification from the league and nullification of any points and/or rewards earned.
Provided battle tag, discord ID, should match with the accounts the applicant uses during the League.
Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora 2025 will take place June 4-7th! Clement "Clem" Desplanches returns to defend his 2024 title against all the top contenders!
Esports Business League is a gaming event for your office! Build better team bonds by friendly or competitive gaming, or get your team to compete against other companies to show how good you are!

Recruit your team and manage your team member roles, team strategies, practice times and more. The only online Counter-Strike strategy editor freely available to everyone! Discuss public strategies with everyone and build private strategies for your team.

Bellum Gens is a gaming and esports event organizer and consultant focused on the development and popularization of esports in Bulgaria. We want to make esports a recognizable topic for the business and thus to help the development of all esports project in Bulgaria and on the Balkans. If you take interest in esports and want to advertise through esports, position your brand in tournaments, streams, or other gaming and esports channels, then we can help! Contact us for more information on available opportunities.

Bellum Gens is the organizer of the premier Bellum Gen Elite esports event. First held in the town of Stara Zagora, under the name Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora, BGE brought the top Counter-Strike talent in the region to compete under one roof for a prize pool of $10,000! Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora 2024 features top StarCraft II players from around the world with a prize pool of €10000!

Bellum Gens is the organizer of the Esports Business League - a competitive amateur gaming event for the office. Miltiple companies in Bulgaria participated in seasons one and two of the Esports Business League both for fun and team building and to show which company has the best gamers among their employees!

Bellum Gens offers a Counter-Strike team finding and team management application, which allows players to look for teams matching their skill and availability, and team owners to manage their teams' roster and general organization. Because Counter-Strike is a team game!

🌟We are thrilled to present Visit Stara Zagora as the main official partner of Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora! This partnership marks a significant step forward in enhancing the development of esports in Bulgaria and raising awareness of Stara Zagora as a premier esports destination in the country.🌟

Stara Zagora is a real treasure trove for researchers. Here you can walk around the home of people who lived 8,000 years ago, walk along a fully preserved ancient street of the Roman city of Augusta Trayana, feel the spirit of the Renaissance and embark on many other exploratory missions. The city is extremely convenient for visiting and walking with an organized group.
Together, we aim to create a vibrant esports community and provide unparalleled opportunities for gamers and fans alike. 🎮

🎉We are thrilled to announce that BulStream is the official production partner of Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora! 🏆 BulStream has exclusively secured production for all events hosted by Bellum Gens - Esports Business League and Bellum Gens Elite.

With their world-class production capabilities and exceptional live streaming services, BulStream is dedicated to delivering the highest quality esports experience to all viewers. Get ready for an unparalleled esports journey! 🎮✨
Together, we aim to achieve top-tier production quality and deliver the ultimate esports experience for both players and audiences! 🚀
🎉 We are thrilled to announce our new strategic partnership with PCBuild! 🖥️✨

PCBuild specializes in assembling high-performance gaming configurations and is dedicated to supporting Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora 2025 and the esports community by providing gamers with the highest quality equipment possible. With their cutting-edge technology, expertly built systems, and commitment to excellence, PCBuild empowers players to realize their full potential and achieve greatness in the competitive gaming world. 🎮🏆
Together, we aim to elevate the esports experience and bring unparalleled performance to our players and fans!
🎉🎓 Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora 2025 and HealthyGG Announce New Academic Research Partnership! 🖥️✨

We are thrilled to announce an exciting new partnership between Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora 2025 and HealthyGG. This collaboration aims to integrate academic excellence with insights on performance, and broadcast technology. 🎮🏆⚕️

During BGE Stara Zagora we will host Andrzej Białecki, a PhD student at Warsaw University of Technology, and previously Józef Piłsudski University of Physical Education in Warsaw. He strives to learn more about various aspects of esports, and how to inform players to become better.
We will leverage a system designed to display the live heart rate of the players to see how they react to the in-game stimuli. This system was designed by Andrzej with assistance of Marcin Warda.
The live capture system was first introduced at a Polish tournament by Daniel Grabka.

🎉 We are thrilled to announce that ASRock has partnered with Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora 2025 to bring you an unforgettable esports experience! This collaboration marks a significant milestone in the world of competitive gaming, combining ASRock's cutting-edge technology with the high-energy atmosphere of Bellum Gens Elite. 🖥️✨

About ASRock: Founded in 2002, ASRock Inc. is a leading Taiwanese manufacturer specializing in motherboards, industrial PCs, and home theater PCs (HTPC). Known for its innovative designs and high-quality products, ASRock has established itself as a major player in the global computer hardware industry. With a commitment to providing top-tier gaming solutions, ASRock's Phantom Gaming product line caters to gamers, professionals, and PC enthusiasts alike. 🎮🏆

Together, ASRock and Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora 2025 aim to elevate the esports experience to new heights, providing gamers and fans with state-of-the-art technology and thrilling gameplay. Stay tuned for more updates and join us in celebrating this exciting partnership!

🎉 We are thrilled to announce a partnership between DeepCool, a leading innovator in computer hardware and cooling solutions, and Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora 2025, Bulgaria's premier esports event. 🖥️🥶✨

About DeepCool: Founded in 1996 and headquartered in Beijing, DeepCool has been at the forefront of providing high-performance cooling parts and thermal solutions globally. With a commitment to innovation and quality, DeepCool's product range includes air and water CPU coolers, computer cases, power supplies, and various computer peripherals. Their dedication to sustainability and excellence is evident through their ISO14000 environmental management standards and continuous improvements in energy-saving and consumption reduction. 🎮🏆

This partnership aims to enhance the esports experience by integrating DeepCool's cutting-edge technology with the thrilling competition of Bellum Gens Elite. Together, we are committed to pushing the boundaries of performance and entertainment, ensuring that both players and fans enjoy the best possible gaming environment.
